<div style="font-size:1.7em; font-weight:bold">Welcome to the <span class="plainlinks">[http://www.openttd.org/ OpenTTD]</span> [http://wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki Wiki]</div>
A user-edited manual and development guide for users and developers of the [http://www.opensource.org/ open source] [[en/Archive/OpenTTD/Transport Tycoon Deluxe]] clone.
