The graphics section is where artists, NewGFX engine coders, and other graphics related developers collaborate on graphics development. Find out about the latest developments in base graphics, [[en/Manual/NewGRF|NewGrfs]] (both 8bpp and [[en/Community/NewGRF/Playing with 32 bpp graphics| 32bpp]]) and more. Also, don't forget to check the Player Resources section below for other graphics-related resources.
